    <div class="container">
      <h2>Things to Know</h2>
      <h3>Medication Reminders Page</h3>
      <p>This page contains all of your reminders</p>
      <p>You can edit or delete the current reminders by pressing edit, and selecting the wrench to adjust a reminder or the trashcan to delete it.</p>
      <p>You can also turn turn off all or specific reminders here temporarily, note, however, that these will reset every day in case one forgets to turn them on.</p>
      <h3>Add Page</h3>
      <p>Use this page to add a new reminder.</p>
      <h3>Settings Page</h3>
      <p>Here, you can change the size of the text for easier visibility. </p>
      <p>You can also use this page to permanently turn off all notifications, that is reminders, on this application, until one decides to turn them on.</p>
      <h3>Recover Reminder Page</h3>
      <p>This page contains all your past reminders, where you can recover any one that you'd like.</p>
